00:31:06,600 --> 00:31:07,480
 argumentirano.

628
00:31:07,480 --> 00:31:07,940
 Znači,

629
00:31:07,940 --> 00:31:08,880
 ubijat ćemo

630
00:31:08,880 --> 00:31:09,920
 njihove laži

631
00:31:09,920 --> 00:31:11,200
 argumentima.

632
00:31:11,200 --> 00:31:12,780
 Argumentima.

633
00:31:12,780 --> 00:31:14,640
 Spomenuli ste malo prije

634
00:31:14,640 --> 00:31:16,980
 čudne kašljeve

635
00:31:16,980 --> 00:31:17,880
 koji traju dugo,

636
00:31:17,880 --> 00:31:18,780
 suhi kašalj.

637
00:31:18,780 --> 00:31:19,080
 Evo,

638
00:31:19,460 --> 00:31:20,580
 nekolicinu ljudi znam

639
00:31:20,580 --> 00:31:21,700
 na primjer baš ove zime

640
00:31:21,700 --> 00:31:23,040
 tuže se i ove nikako

641
00:31:23,040 --> 00:31:24,200
 da im prestane kašalj.

642
00:31:24,200 --> 00:31:24,580
 Ali dobro,

643
00:31:24,580 --> 00:31:25,040
 to je možda

644
00:31:25,040 --> 00:31:25,120
 i slučajnost.

645
00:31:25,120 --> 00:31:26,120
 I mene je sad držalo

646
00:31:26,120 --> 00:31:26,680
 pet dana,

647
00:31:26,680 --> 00:31:27,400
 sad sam jeo,

648
00:31:27,400 --> 00:31:28,560
 sad mi je nešto lakše.

649
00:31:28,560 --> 00:31:29,800
 Ali kažu da slučajnosti

650
00:31:29,800 --> 00:31:30,780
 zapravo ne postoje.

651
00:31:30,780 --> 00:31:31,000
 Da.

652
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:31,500
 No dobro.

653
00:31:31,500 --> 00:31:32,680
 S druge strane,

654
00:31:32,680 --> 00:31:33,180
 rekli ste,

655
00:31:33,180 --> 00:31:34,180
 napada se zdravlje.

656
00:31:34,180 --> 00:31:37,060
 Psiha,

657
00:31:37,060 --> 00:31:37,880
 ljudi su nekako

658
00:31:37,880 --> 00:31:38,900
 sve anemičniji,

659
00:31:38,900 --> 00:31:39,580
 rekla bih.

660
00:31:39,580 --> 00:31:40,800
 Sve su nekako

661
00:31:40,800 --> 00:31:42,000
 nezainteresirani

662
00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:43,060
 za sve oko sebe.

663
00:31:43,180 --> 00:31:45,140
 sve su ne znam,

664
00:31:45,140 --> 00:31:47,300
 onako mlaki su.

665
00:31:47,300 --> 00:31:48,140
 Onda imamo

666
00:31:48,140 --> 00:31:49,440
 izuzetno velik

667
00:31:49,440 --> 00:31:50,600
 porast tumora

668
00:31:50,600 --> 00:31:52,100
 kod ljudi.

669
00:31:52,100 --> 00:31:53,060
 Možemo li

670
00:31:53,060 --> 00:31:54,600
 taj porast

671
00:31:54,600 --> 00:31:56,040
 tih broja tumora,

672
00:31:56,040 --> 00:31:57,040
 ali i sveg lošeg

673
00:31:57,040 --> 00:31:57,980
 zdravstvenog stanja,

674
00:31:58,380 --> 00:31:59,300
 dovesti u vezu

675
00:31:59,300 --> 00:32:00,360
 sa zrakom

676
00:32:00,360 --> 00:32:01,100
 koji dišemo,

677
00:32:01,100 --> 00:32:02,520
 sa vodom koju pijemo

678
00:32:02,520 --> 00:32:03,680
 ili sa tlom

679
00:32:03,680 --> 00:32:04,520
 ne znam,

680
00:32:04,520 --> 00:32:05,700
 iz kojeg dobivamo

681
00:32:05,700 --> 00:32:06,500
 salatu,

682
00:32:06,500 --> 00:32:07,900
 rajčicu.

683
00:32:07,900 --> 00:32:09,600
 Ali ne samo to,

684
00:32:09,600 --> 00:32:10,980
 nego ljudi nisu svjesni

685
00:32:10,980 --> 00:32:12,260
 da možda zbog

686
00:32:12,260 --> 00:32:13,960
 svoje komocije

687
00:32:13,960 --> 00:32:14,640
 ili ne znam čega

688
00:32:14,640 --> 00:32:15,300
 kad kupuju

689
00:32:15,300 --> 00:32:16,560
 nekakve namirnice

690
00:32:16,560 --> 00:32:18,240
 u trgovačkim tim lancima,

691
00:32:18,240 --> 00:32:20,000
 ne znam koliko

692
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:20,540
 i se pita

693
00:32:20,540 --> 00:32:21,700
 kolika je kvaliteta

694
00:32:21,700 --> 00:32:22,660
 i kemijska

695
00:32:22,660 --> 00:32:23,640
 i biološka

696
00:32:23,640 --> 00:32:24,680
 i energetska

697
00:32:24,680 --> 00:32:25,540
 tih namirnica.

698
00:32:25,540 --> 00:32:26,480
 Mislim da je tu

699
00:32:26,480 --> 00:32:27,320
 jedan od glavnih,

700
00:32:27,320 --> 00:32:28,280
 isto jedan od glavnih

701
00:32:28,280 --> 00:32:28,940
 uzročnika

702
00:32:28,940 --> 00:32:30,640
 o čemu vi govorite.

703
00:32:30,640 --> 00:32:31,360
 Znači,

704
00:32:31,360 --> 00:32:32,960
 postoje li neki podaci

705
00:32:32,960 --> 00:32:33,860
 gospodine Kemiću

706
00:32:33,860 --> 00:32:35,580
 što mi pijemo,

707
00:32:35,580 --> 00:32:37,020
 kakva nam je kišnica,

708
00:32:37,020 --> 00:32:38,060
 kakav nam je zrak,

709
00:32:38,060 --> 00:32:39,160
 kako nam ovo

710
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:40,740
 dolazi s neba

711
00:32:40,740 --> 00:32:41,640
 na naše glave,

712
00:32:41,640 --> 00:32:42,000
 ne znam.

713
00:32:42,000 --> 00:32:44,860
 Radi li to netko ozbiljan?

714
00:32:44,860 --> 00:32:45,280
 Reci mu u Hrvatskoj.

715
00:32:45,280 --> 00:32:46,100
 Evo, mi smo sad

716
00:32:46,100 --> 00:32:46,840
 u sklopu

717
00:32:46,840 --> 00:32:48,800
 instituta za bio i tehnosferu

718
00:32:48,800 --> 00:32:50,720
 u kojem sam ja sad predsjednik.

719
00:32:50,720 --> 00:32:52,820
 Znači, mi smo pred dvije godine,

720
00:32:52,820 --> 00:32:53,820
 evo sad smo napravili

721
00:32:53,820 --> 00:32:55,240
 tu jednu preliminarnu analizu,

722
00:32:55,240 --> 00:32:56,540
 čisto početno da vidimo

723
00:32:56,540 --> 00:32:58,120
 na veliki raspon,

724
00:32:58,120 --> 00:32:59,620
 ono, bilo ih jedno dvadeset,

725
00:32:59,620 --> 00:32:59,920
 mislim,

726
00:32:59,920 --> 00:33:01,340
 ili koliko teških metala,

727
00:33:01,340 --> 00:33:02,400
 da vidimo

728
00:33:02,400 --> 00:33:03,800
 koje su koncentracije.

729
00:33:03,800 --> 00:33:05,660
 I htjeli smo to uspoređiti

730
00:33:05,660 --> 00:33:06,600
 sa ovim uzorcima,

731
00:33:06,600 --> 00:33:08,140
 odnosno uzorkovanjem u Bosni,

732
00:33:08,140 --> 00:33:08,700
 što je isto

733
00:33:08,700 --> 00:33:09,980
 bilo napravljeno,

734
00:33:09,980 --> 00:33:11,180
 jer se tvrdilo da kao

735
00:33:11,180 --> 00:33:12,820
 kad se tu pojave

736
00:33:12,820 --> 00:33:14,160
 neke čudne stvari na nebu,

737
00:33:14,160 --> 00:33:14,620
 da je to,

738
00:33:14,620 --> 00:33:15,240
 ne znam,

739
00:33:15,240 --> 00:33:16,340
 saharski pjesak.

740
00:33:16,720 --> 00:33:17,640
 I onda se lijepo vidjelo

741
00:33:17,640 --> 00:33:18,980
 iz njihove analize u Bosni,

742
00:33:18,980 --> 00:33:20,640
 da to nije saharski pjesak,

743
00:33:20,640 --> 00:33:22,180
 da su koncentracije teških metala

744
00:33:22,180 --> 00:33:23,120
 brutalno veće.

745
00:33:23,120 --> 00:33:24,980
 I mi smo isto tako našli.

746
00:33:24,980 --> 00:33:26,740
 Znači, u tom našem uzorkovanju,

747
00:33:26,740 --> 00:33:29,000
 to je bilo na lokacijama Split,

748
00:33:29,000 --> 00:33:30,780
 Zagreb, Bjelovar.

749
00:33:30,780 --> 00:33:33,100
 Znači, u Splitu je bio suhi uzorak,

750
00:33:33,100 --> 00:33:34,760
 uzet sa površine,

751
00:33:34,760 --> 00:33:36,300
 konkretno sauta,

752
00:33:36,300 --> 00:33:38,840
 a ova druga dva uzorka

753
00:33:38,840 --> 00:33:39,760
 su bila tekuća.

754
00:33:39,760 --> 00:33:41,360
 Znači, uzeto je u posude

755
00:33:41,360 --> 00:33:43,100
 i poslano u laboratoriji.

756
00:33:43,100 --> 00:33:43,660
 I to, ono,

757
00:33:43,660 --> 00:33:45,080
 certificirani laboratori

758
00:33:45,080 --> 00:33:46,340
 i oni su napravili analizu.

759
00:33:46,340 --> 00:33:48,080
 Imali smo povećanje,

760
00:33:48,080 --> 00:33:49,100
 znači, stroncija,

761
00:33:49,100 --> 00:33:50,240
 barija, aluminija,

762
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:52,720
 velika količina željeza,

763
00:33:52,720 --> 00:33:55,360
 bilo i drugih teških metala.

764
00:33:55,360 --> 00:33:57,360
 Što oni čine našem tijelu zdravi?

765
00:33:57,360 --> 00:33:58,280
 Oni su otrovni.

766
00:33:58,280 --> 00:33:59,520
 Znači, konkretno,

767
00:33:59,520 --> 00:34:00,000
 ne znam,

768
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:01,260
 ali ne samo za nas.

769
00:34:01,260 --> 00:34:02,460
 Recimo, stroncivam je

770
00:34:02,460 --> 00:34:03,700
 katastrofa za biljke.

771
00:34:03,700 --> 00:34:05,120
 Znači, ono totalno poremeti

772
00:34:05,120 --> 00:34:06,880
 metabolizam vode kod biljaka

773
00:34:06,880 --> 00:34:08,260
 i sušivanja,

774
00:34:08,260 --> 00:34:09,700
 recimo, naročito crnogorica,

775
00:34:09,700 --> 00:34:11,700
 što sad ljudi dosta primjećuju

776
00:34:11,700 --> 00:34:12,360
 da se zbiva.

777
00:34:12,360 --> 00:34:13,460
 Šume umiru.

778
00:34:13,460 --> 00:34:13,740
 Da.

779
00:34:13,740 --> 00:34:15,080
 Znači, očito,

780
00:34:15,080 --> 00:34:17,400
 znači, to je samo jedan mali uzorak.

781
00:34:17,400 --> 00:34:18,980
 Zapravo, mi namjeravamo

782
00:34:18,980 --> 00:34:19,640
 puno veći,

783
00:34:19,640 --> 00:34:21,500
 statistički značajniji uzorak uzet

784
00:34:21,500 --> 00:34:22,040
 da vidimo

785
00:34:22,040 --> 00:34:24,700
 distribuirano po čitovoj Hrvatskoj

786
00:34:24,700 --> 00:34:25,900
 kako se to ponaša.

787
00:34:25,900 --> 00:34:28,340
 Neki laboratori su radili

788
00:34:28,340 --> 00:34:29,220
 ozbiljnije analize.

789
00:34:29,220 --> 00:34:30,240
 Ja sam vidio u Splitu,

790
00:34:30,240 --> 00:34:31,180
 recimo, su napravili

791
00:34:31,180 --> 00:34:32,020
 jednu jako dobru

792
00:34:32,020 --> 00:34:33,240
 i ozbiljnu analizu

793
00:34:33,240 --> 00:34:34,120
 koja isto upućuje

794
00:34:34,120 --> 00:34:36,160
 u sličnom smjeru,

795
00:34:36,160 --> 00:34:37,140
 na sličnom zaključak,

796
00:34:37,140 --> 00:34:38,180
 da nam je zapravo

797
00:34:38,180 --> 00:34:39,460
 kišnica kontaminirana.

798
00:34:39,460 --> 00:34:40,820
 Znači, ovi ljudi u lici

799
00:34:40,820 --> 00:34:41,660
 koji još uvek koriste

800
00:34:41,660 --> 00:34:42,920
 kišnicu za pitku vodu,

801
00:34:42,920 --> 00:34:44,340
 priporučio bih im

802
00:34:44,340 --> 00:34:45,400
 da to ne čine više.

803
00:34:45,400 --> 00:34:47,740
 Čisto da zaštite

804
00:34:47,740 --> 00:34:48,440
 svoje zdravlje.

805
00:34:48,600 --> 00:34:49,880
 A na području bivše države

806
00:34:49,880 --> 00:34:52,480
 gdje je najviše upaljinara

807
00:34:52,480 --> 00:34:52,960
 alarm?

808
00:34:52,960 --> 00:34:54,360
 Gdje je najviše crveno

809
00:34:54,360 --> 00:34:56,680
 po tom pitanju blica?

810
00:34:56,680 --> 00:34:58,340
 Hrvatska, Bosna, Srbija,

811
00:34:58,340 --> 00:34:59,040
 ne znam, Slovenija?

812
00:34:59,040 --> 00:35:00,380
 Mislim da je tu nejako,

813
00:35:00,380 --> 00:35:01,300
 ali tu je bilo

814
00:35:01,300 --> 00:35:03,380
 periodičkih nekakvih promjena.

815
00:35:03,380 --> 00:35:04,520
 Znači, mislim da su

816
00:35:04,520 --> 00:35:06,020
 čak na karti

817
00:35:06,020 --> 00:35:07,840
 Evropske agencije za okoliš,

818
00:35:07,840 --> 00:35:10,460
 European Environmental Agency,

819
00:35:10,460 --> 00:35:12,120
 na njihovoj službenoj karti,

820
00:35:12,120 --> 00:35:13,240
 mislim za 2021.

821
00:35:13,240 --> 00:35:14,300
 ili tu negdje,

822
00:35:15,340 --> 00:35:16,800
 kad oni stave,

823
00:35:16,800 --> 00:35:18,880
 znači, oni su analizirali

824
00:35:18,880 --> 00:35:21,460
 rizik,

825
00:35:21,460 --> 00:35:22,580
 pozdravlje,

826
00:35:22,580 --> 00:35:24,180
 s obzirom na zagađenost

827
00:35:24,180 --> 00:35:26,180
 česticama ispod 2,5 mikrometra,

828
00:35:26,180 --> 00:35:27,400
 to je ono, PM2,5.

829
00:35:27,400 --> 00:35:29,540
 I oni su napravili kartu

830
00:35:29,540 --> 00:35:30,520
 zagađenosti,

831
00:35:30,520 --> 00:35:31,480
 u smislu rizika.

832
00:35:31,480 --> 00:35:33,300
 Znači, koliko se skraćuje

833
00:35:33,300 --> 00:35:34,500
 životni vijek ljudi,

834
00:35:34,500 --> 00:35:36,440
 s obzirom na te koncentracije.

835
00:35:36,440 --> 00:35:38,200
 I oni su,

836
00:35:38,200 --> 00:35:40,420
 u toj karti možete vidjeti,

837
00:35:40,420 --> 00:35:42,100
 da je zapravo najbrutalnije

838
00:35:42,100 --> 00:35:44,020
 zagađena Srbija,

839
00:35:44,560 --> 00:35:45,780
 Bosna, Makedonija,

840
00:35:45,780 --> 00:35:46,500
 Bugarska,

841
00:35:46,500 --> 00:35:47,820
 prema Rumunjskoj

842
00:35:47,820 --> 00:35:48,840
 i Hrvatska.

843
00:35:48,840 --> 00:35:50,240
 Znači, ona nije toliko

844
00:35:50,240 --> 00:35:51,500
 koliko Srbija,

845
00:35:51,500 --> 00:35:52,740
 po njihovom tom ne,

846
00:35:52,740 --> 00:35:53,940
 ali ja ne bih rekao

847
00:35:53,940 --> 00:35:54,640
 da smo mi nešto

848
00:35:54,640 --> 00:35:55,640
 tu u bolje pozicije,

849
00:35:55,640 --> 00:35:58,160
 jer dijelimo istu situaciju,

850
00:35:58,160 --> 00:36:00,020
 kad se promatra realno.

851
00:36:00,020 --> 00:36:02,040
 Zapravo dijelimo isto nebo.

852
00:36:02,040 --> 00:36:03,140
 Isto nebo, da.

853
00:36:03,140 --> 00:36:04,240
 Nema na njemu

854
00:36:04,240 --> 00:36:04,460
 onih državnih granica.

855
00:36:04,460 --> 00:36:05,300
 I zapravo, znači,

856
00:36:05,300 --> 00:36:06,320
 tu se lijepo vidi,

857
00:36:06,320 --> 00:36:06,780
 već znači,

858
00:36:06,780 --> 00:36:08,080
 službeni taj dokument,

859
00:36:08,080 --> 00:36:09,660
 službena karta vam pokazuje

860
00:36:09,660 --> 00:36:10,420
 da se tu nešto

861
00:36:10,420 --> 00:36:11,540
 neobičnu domađu.

862
00:36:11,540 --> 00:36:12,120
 A da li ti službe...

863
00:36:12,120 --> 00:36:13,360
 Znači, ovo je najzagađeniji

864
00:36:13,360 --> 00:36:14,620
 dio ovog svijeta.

865
00:36:14,620 --> 00:36:16,140
 Znači, sad vam je

866
00:36:16,140 --> 00:36:17,320
 pred par, ne znam koliko,

867
00:36:17,320 --> 00:36:18,220
 pred jedan dana,

868
00:36:18,220 --> 00:36:19,900
 ja sam gledao IQR-ovu kartu,

869
00:36:19,900 --> 00:36:21,240
 oni imaju onu listu

870
00:36:21,240 --> 00:36:22,860
 najzagađenijih gradova svijeta.

871
00:36:22,860 --> 00:36:24,700
 Prvo, drugo, ne znam, mjesto.

872
00:36:24,700 --> 00:36:26,280
 Sarajevo je bilo

873
00:36:26,280 --> 00:36:27,800
 najzagađeniji grad na svijetu.

874
00:36:27,800 --> 00:36:29,060
 Na prvom mjestu,

875
00:36:29,060 --> 00:36:30,360
 sad pred nekih tjedan dana.

876
00:36:30,360 --> 00:36:31,300
 Ne mogu vam sad reći

877
00:36:31,300 --> 00:36:32,040
 točno datum.

878
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:33,600
 Hrvatska je, mislim,

879
00:36:33,600 --> 00:36:34,900
 sa Zagrebom bila,

880
00:36:34,900 --> 00:36:35,900
 Zagreb je bio negdje,

881
00:36:35,900 --> 00:36:36,720
 mislim, na 16.

882
00:36:36,720 --> 00:36:38,200
 Ispred Vuhana,

883
00:36:38,200 --> 00:36:40,240
 hiperindustrijskog grada.

884
00:36:40,240 --> 00:36:42,380
 Mislim, o čemu mi pričalo.

885
00:36:42,380 --> 00:36:43,960
 Da, onda kažu, ne znam,

886
00:36:43,960 --> 00:36:45,940
 Sarajevo je dole u Kotlini,

887
00:36:45,940 --> 00:36:47,680
 pa se sve spusti dole.

888
00:36:47,680 --> 00:36:48,280
 To je istina.

889
00:36:48,280 --> 00:36:49,460
 Znači, oni imaju kronično

890
00:36:49,460 --> 00:36:50,120
 taj problem

891
00:36:50,120 --> 00:36:51,600
 i dio, znači,

892
00:36:51,600 --> 00:36:52,380
 i od industrije,

893
00:36:52,380 --> 00:36:53,360
 od fosilne gorijeva,

894
00:36:53,360 --> 00:36:53,840
 tih stvari.

895
00:36:53,840 --> 00:36:54,260
 Što je onda, recimo,

896
00:36:54,260 --> 00:36:55,460
 u Zagrebu ili, ne znam,

